description:
As a coffee buyer
  I want a coffee machine that
  I can put coins in and get change back
   or pay with bank card
  and get a cup of Americano back
  with sugar or without sugar
  because I like Americano and crave caffeine.

elements.name: buy Americano without sugar with coins

steps.name: that the machine is plugged in
that water is available
that the machine has enough  coffee for a cup
the machine has plastic cups
the user presses the "Americano" button
the user inserts a 10 kr coin
the user inserts a 10 kr coin
the user inserts a 0 kr coin
the user inserts a 0 kr coin
presses the "start" button
the user recieves 1 cup of Americano.
